  <body>
    <h1>Our First Team Project: A Book Sharing App for GIMM Students!</h1>
    <p>The App itself is not published yet, but when it is, we will post it here! For now, you can go ahead and experience our <a href="index.html">map</a> part of our app that shows geological location!</p>
    <p> How the App functions: when a user has a book that they wish to give away, they post a listing onto the app that goes into an actively updated listings page. From there, users that are browsing books can find what they are looking for as well as find contact information to get in contact with the user giving that book away. When they come to an agreement and wish to meet up with them, the person giving the book away has an option to pin their location using Google Maps Geolocation data and saving it to our app. The other user can access this data by going to the map and finding and clicking on either their pin, or the listing accompanied with their pin. After they have met up, they can delete their pin and their listing, or mark it as unavailable after editing it.</p>
